<!doctype html>
<html lang="de">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1" />
  <meta name="description" content="AvaloniaERP – Mini-ERP mit Avalonia (MVVM), EF Core und SQLite." />
  <title>AvaloniaERP</title>

  <style>
    :root{
      --bg:#0b0f14; --panel:#101824; --text:#e7eef7; --muted:#9fb0c3;
      --accent:#7cc4ff; --accent2:#a2ffcc; --line:rgba(255,255,255,.10);
      --shadow: 0 16px 40px rgba(0,0,0,.35);
      --radius: 18px;
      --max: 1050px;
    }
    @media (prefers-color-scheme: light){
      :root{ --bg:#f6f8fb; --panel:#ffffff; --text:#0b1220; --muted:#516176; --line:rgba(0,0,0,.10); --shadow: 0 16px 40px rgba(0,0,0,.10); }
    }
    *{box-sizing:border-box}
    body{
      margin:0; font:16px/1.55 system-ui,-apple-system,Segoe UI,Roboto,Ubuntu,Cantarell,Noto Sans,sans-serif;
      background: radial-gradient(1200px 600px at 20% 0%, rgba(124,196,255,.18), transparent 60%),
                  radial-gradient(1000px 500px at 80% 10%, rgba(162,255,204,.14), transparent 55%),
                  var(--bg);
      color:var(--text);
    }
    a{color:inherit}
    .wrap{max-width:var(--max); margin:0 auto; padding:28px 18px 60px}
    header{display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:space-between; gap:12px; padding:10px 0 22px}
    .brand{display:flex; gap:12px; align-items:center; text-decoration:none}
    .logo{
      width:38px; height:38px; border-radius:12px;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg,var(--accent),var(--accent2));
      box-shadow: var(--shadow);
    }
    .brand b{font-size:18px}
    .brand span{display:block; color:var(--muted); font-size:13px; margin-top:2px}

    .pillbar{display:flex; flex-wrap:wrap; gap:10px; justify-content:flex-end}
    .pill{
      text-decoration:none; padding:8px 12px; border-radius:999px;
      border:1px solid var(--line); background: rgba(255,255,255,.04);
    }
    .pill:hover{border-color: rgba(124,196,255,.55)}

    .hero{
      display:grid; grid-template-columns: 1.2fr .8fr; gap:18px;
      align-items:stretch; margin-top:6px;
    }
    @media (max-width: 900px){ .hero{grid-template-columns:1fr} }

    .card{
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(255,255,255,.06), rgba(255,255,255,.02));
      border:1px solid var(--line);
      border-radius: var(--radius);
      box-shadow: var(--shadow);
      padding:22px;
    }
    h1{margin:0 0 10px; font-size:42px; line-height:1.06; letter-spacing:-.02em}
    @media (max-width: 520px){ h1{font-size:34px} }
    .subtitle{color:var(--muted); margin:0 0 18px; font-size:16px}
    .cta{display:flex; flex-wrap:wrap; gap:10px; margin-top:14px}
    .btn{
      text-decoration:none; padding:10px 14px; border-radius:12px;
      border:1px solid var(--line); background: rgba(255,255,255,.05);
      display:inline-flex; gap:10px; align-items:center;
    }
    .btn.primary{
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(124,196,255,.24), rgba(162,255,204,.18));
      border-color: rgba(124,196,255,.50);
    }
    .btn:hover{transform: translateY(-1px)}
    .btn small{color:var(--muted)}

    .grid{display:grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(12, 1fr); gap:14px; margin-top:14px}
    .col6{grid-column: span 6}
    .col4{grid-column: span 4}
    .col12{grid-column: span 12}
    @media (max-width: 900px){ .col6,.col4{grid-column: span 12} }

    h2{margin:0 0 10px; font-size:18px}
    ul{margin:10px 0 0; padding-left:18px; color:var(--muted)}
    li{margin:6px 0}
    code,kbd{font-family: ui-monospace,SFMono-Regular,Menlo,Monaco,Consolas,monospace}
    .meta{
      display:flex; flex-wrap:wrap; gap:8px; margin-top:12px;
      color:var(--muted); font-size:13px
    }
    .tag{
      border:1px solid var(--line); border-radius:999px; padding:5px 10px;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,.03);
    }
    footer{margin-top:22px; color:var(--muted); font-size:13px; text-align:center}
    .sep{height:1px; background:var(--line); margin:18px 0}
  </style>
</head>

<body>
  <div class="wrap">
    <header>
      <a class="brand" href="https://github.com/maxBernd661/AvaloniaERP" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">
        <div class="logo" aria-hidden="true"></div>
        <div>
          <b>AvaloniaERP</b>
          <span>Mini-ERP: Kunden, Artikel, Bestellungen</span>
        </div>
      </a>

      <nav class="pillbar">
        <a class="pill" href="erModel.pdf">ER-Modell (PDF)</a>
        <a class="pill" href="tables.sql">SQL Schema</a>
        <a class="pill" href="https://github.com/maxBernd661/AvaloniaERP/releases/latest" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">Release</a>
      </nav>
    </header>

    <section class="hero">
      <div class="card">
        <h1>ERP, aber klein genug, dass man es noch versteht.</h1>
        <p class="subtitle">
          AvaloniaERP ist ein Desktop-Mini-ERP mit Avalonia (MVVM) im .NET Generic Host,
          EF Core und SQLite. Fokus: saubere Service-Architektur statt “alles im Code-Behind, wird schon”.
        </p>

        <div class="cta">
          <a class="btn primary" href="https://github.com/maxBernd661/AvaloniaERP" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">
            <span>GitHub Repo</span>
            <small>Code & Doku</small>
          </a>
          <a class="btn" href="https://github.com/maxBernd661/AvaloniaERP/releases/latest" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">
            <span>Latest Release</span>
            <small>Download</small>
          </a>
          <a class="btn" href="#architektur">
            <span>Architektur</span>
            <small>Überblick</small>
          </a>
        </div>

        <div class="meta">
          <span class="tag">Avalonia MVVM</span>
          <span class="tag">EF Core</span>
          <span class="tag">SQLite</span>
          <span class="tag">Generic Host</span>
          <span class="tag">Unit Tests</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <h2>Projektstruktur</h2>
        <ul>
          <li><code>AvaloniaERP.Win</code> – Frontend (Avalonia MVVM)</li>
          <li><code>AvaloniaERP.Core</code> – Backend (EF Core + SQLite)</li>
          <li><code>AvaloniaERP.Core.Test</code> – Tests (Auditing/Soft-Delete)</li>
        </ul>

        <div class="sep"></div>

        <h2>Schnellstart</h2>
        <ul>
          <li><code>dotnet test AvaloniaERP.Core.Test/AvaloniaERP.Core.Test.csproj</code></li>
          <li>Datenbankpfad: <code>AvaloniaERP.Win/appsettings.json</code></li>
          <li>Migrationen: via EF Core (siehe Repo)</li>
        </ul>

        <div class="sep"></div>

        <h2>Artefakte</h2>
        <ul>
          <li><a href="erModel.pdf">ER-Modell (PDF)</a></li>
          <li><a href="tables.sql">SQL Tabellen (DDL)</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="architektur" class="grid">
      <div class="card col6">
        <h2>Backend (Core)</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>Entitäten in <code>AvaloniaERP.Core/Entity</code></li>
          <li><code>EntityContext</code>: CRUD, Zeitstempel, Soft-Deletes</li>
          <li><code>IQueryProfile&lt;T&gt;</code>: Ladeverhalten/Includes</li>
          <li><code>IGraphMerger&lt;T&gt;</code>: Speichern komplexer Objektgraphen</li>
          <li><code>RowBase&lt;T&gt;</code>: DTOs fürs UI</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="card col6">
        <h2>Frontend (Win)</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>Avalonia MVVM auf .NET Generic Host</li>
          <li>Service-basiert: Navigation & VM-Erstellung</li>
          <li><code>IViewModelFactory</code>, <code>INavigationService</code></li>
          <li>CRUD über <code>IDataManipulationService</code></li>
          <li>Views via XAML</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="card col12">
        <h2>Warum existiert das?</h2>
        <p style="margin:0;color:var(--muted)">
          Weil “Mini-ERP” ein perfekter Prüfungsprojekt-Klassiker ist: genug Domäne für echte Beziehungen,
          genug UI für echtes MVVM, und genug Datenbank für echte Fehler. Und weil Menschen gerne leiden.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <footer>
      © <span id="y"></span> AvaloniaERP · Statisch gehostet über GitHub Pages ·
      <a href="https://github.com/maxBernd661/AvaloniaERP" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">Repository</a>
    </footer>
  </div>

  <script>
    document.getElementById("y").textContent = new Date().getFullYear();
  </script>
</body>
</html>
